Project on Ansible+GIT+AWS
===========================
Task Description :
====================
Launch 2 RHEL8 instances in AWS
Configure password-less SSH authentication for EC2 instances
Configure a Control Node locally 
Login to your github account and create a Repository called RH294
Install git client on the Control node. Create an index.html file and push the file into the remote github repository.
Write an Ansible Playbook to perform the following tasks on the Managed Hosts [ EC2 instances ]
Install httpd and firewalld packages
Start and Enable httpd and firewalld service
Allow http through firewall
Download a custom index.html file from the remote github repository and place it
Within the default Document Root of the web server i.e. /var/www/html

